reward_description: That's right, you get to see the game in it's raw form and help us shape it into a better game for our Beta Tester Backers to play after the Kickstarter campaign ends. In exchange, you will receive 3 times the value of your donation of 100 dollars or more in Gold Bars to use in the game once we go LIVE on Facebook. Maximum of 9,000 Gold Bars for 300 dollars. We've done all we can do and now it's time to collaborate and make the game even better! Provide us with your suggestions and comments and help us fine tune the user experience. Legend of Ace - Casino Quest is the first-ever social game, made socially and YOU are the first step in that process. The second step is when we turn it over to our Beta Testers who will then provide us even more feedback and suggestions, making the game even better for the public release. The third step is when we take all that we have accomplished together and launch it on Facebook making it LIVE to the public. The final step is for us to build more levels and make the game available on mobile devices such as IOS and Android. Hitting our stretch goals will allow us to make that happen! Note: You must provide your full name, email, Kickstarter name, and Facebook account name in order to become a developer and start playing the Beta while the Kickstarter campaign is still running. Also you must share your pledge on your Facebook wall and then share your post with the Legend of Ace - Casino Quest page in order for us to confirm you as Backer at this level.

You share a hotel room with me and 2-3 others in my Gen Con crew (most likely my poster/t-shirt printing specialist and my blue Twi'lek "booth babe"), and you party like a game designer (see below) for five glorious nights. The only thing you need is spending money for food and shopping; we'll even pick you up at the airport! ACCOMMODATIONS: We are staying in the Marriott Downtown Indianapolis, directly across the street from the exhibit hall at the convention center (and we even have an elevated skywalk that connects us so we don't even have to cross the street!). Keep in mind, though, you'll be attending the convention the same way we do: Cramming as many people as possible into each hotel room. I will give the owner of the VIP package the option to pick a bed all their own, though, and I hereby volunteer to sleep on the air mattress if no one else will! FLIGHT: As mentioned, the offer is limited to the lower 48 US states just to keep the costs reasonable -- Alaska, Hawaii, and most international flights would cost an arm and a leg. If you're really, really interested and you're coming from farther away, I would chip in the first $300 of the ticket if you're willing to spring for the rest. "PARTYING LIKE A GAME DESIGNER": Game designers don't party very well (we're all socially awkward nerds), but we are prone to playing pick-up games at night in the hotel room. (And drinking. We do tend to drink.)

reward_description: We will do much more than just whisper your name in our ‘Thank You Shout Outs' video, which we’ll post on our YouTube channel! We may even attempt to say thanks in your native language. As an extra thanks we will also give you some pretty HD wallpapers with Midli art, for you phone and desktop!

name: Midli: A Dark and Mystical Tale of Letting Go
reward_description: We don’t know how we’d write your name in the stars, but we sure can write them in our game credits to show off how you helped make Midli possible! We will also give you 1 copy of the game and everything from the 'Whispered in the Wind' tier!

name: Midli: A Dark and Mystical Tale of Letting Go
reward_description: We will let you peek behind the scenes and be the first to try out the game while it’s in BETA. You will even get a closer look at the development process of Midli in our digital booklet ‘The Making of Midli’ with behind the scenes pics, concept art and design notes. Of course all previous tiers are also included.

name: Midli: A Dark and Mystical Tale of Letting Go
reward_description: We will send you a personal 'thank you' postcard from London (consider that the “beyond”) signed by the Midli team. Not just any postcard either, this will feature pretty Midli promo art on a quality glossy postcard. You will also of course receive all of the rewards from previous tiers.

name: Midli: A Dark and Mystical Tale of Letting Go
reward_description: It's thanks to YOU that Midli can be made, so we want you to feel like you’re part of the DinoByte team! You will get a cute DinoByte Labs team enamel pin with our lil' skeleton Dino mascot as well as everything from previous tiers.

name: Midli: A Dark and Mystical Tale of Letting Go
reward_description: Our tarot cards probably won't actually show you the future, but they sure are pretty! As a thanks for backing Midli you will get an exclusive and frankly SUPER COOL set of 6 tarot cards featuring the characters from Midli. The cards will be 55mm x 84mm with rounded corners on glossy 350gsm card stock, and they come in a classy black envelope sealed in wax with the custom DinoByte Labs seal of approval (literally). As if that wasn't cool enough, you will get everything from the previous tiers as well!

name: Midli: A Dark and Mystical Tale of Letting Go
reward_description: Wow! Thank you so much for supporting Midli! In addition to all the amazing and exclusive loot from the previous tiers, you will get an ULTRA THICK (600gsm) high quality Midli art card. This card was specially made in collaboration by DinoByte Labs founders Christian and Louise, just for you lovely KickStarter backers! The card will be printed on high quality textured cardstock (178mm x 127mm) and signed by the artists.

name: Midli: A Dark and Mystical Tale of Letting Go
reward_description: In addition to all the amazing and exclusive loot from the previous tiers, you will get an ULTRA THICK (600gsm) high quality Midli art card. This card was specially made in collaboration by DinoByte Labs founders Christian and Louise, just for you lovely KickStarter backers! The card will be printed on high quality textured cardstock (178mm x 127mm) and signed by the artists.

name: Midli: A Dark and Mystical Tale of Letting Go
reward_description: We’d love to chat with you in a 1 hour video call, and let you get inside our minds! Consider this a 1-on-1 A.M.A. where you can ask us anything from what's it like to be a game dev to what are juicy secrets behind Midli's stories (You will have to sign an NDA for this info since it's very top secret!!) For this reward we can guarantee DinoByte co-founders Chris and Lou for the call, and the possibility of requesting our artist James to join. AND OF COURSE all previous tiers are included.

name: Midli: A Dark and Mystical Tale of Letting Go
reward_description: This is a really unique reward, so it is limited to only 2 backers! You will get to help us create one of the Forgotten Shadow creatures in game. Once it is designed and named, our artist will draw some fancy concept art which you will receive as a one of a kind high quality A4 print, signed on the back by the team. We will also credit you in our game with the badass title of “Mistress/Master of Shadows” (your choice). You will of course also get all of the other great rewards from previous tiers!

name: Augmented Reality Hacky sack
reward_description: We all know that we will grow old and that someday our lives will end. That's why we try so hard to live each day to the fullest. That's why we keep stumbling on by trial and error. But it isn't just for ourselves, it's so we can leave some signposts for the people following in our foot steps. To cowards who cling to where they are and who have given up on trying to move forward, there is no way to see how bright the future is even though it's just around the corner, but you can kick it like a hackysack. You just kicked my sack right in the heart, Thanks. Your name will appear in the list of backers with a super special symbol x2 next to it that shows your better then some.

name: Augmented Reality Hacky sack
reward_description: I think you and I have different concepts of beauty. I was taught that it's beautiful to survive, unsightly or not. Now thanks to you when your ever out there surviving no shall go without a hackysack(as long as they have a smartphone). Your name will appear in the list of backers with a even more special symbol  next to it that shows your better then most.

name: Augmented Reality Hacky sack
reward_description: Relying on someone, helping each other out, and supporting each other. Most would say that's the right thing to do. However, that's just idealistic. In reality, not everyone is willing to donate $1.30 like you. Thanks ever so much for your support, your name will appear in the list of backers with 2 even more special symbols next to it that shows your better then most.

name: Augmented Reality Hacky sack
reward_description: Life is basically like a soap bubble. It rides on the wind, flying here and there... and before you realize it - pop! It's gone. When it's about to disappear, you think that you could've flown a little higher. But by the time, it's already too late. And thanks to you people can pop knowing they always had a hackysack next to them. Thanks so much, your name will appear in the list of backers with a symbol that's a bit bigger then others but still even more special proving your better then most.

name: meQuanics: The Quantum Computer Game
reward_description: You get to submit your own custom quantum circuits to be available for play in the game. You also join us in Tokyo (or Melbourne, wherever the development team may be) for an evening of very confusing talk about quantum technology and the fundamental physics that underly meQuanics. (Travel expenses not included) Date is TBD. Your name included in acknowledgements as a supporter in any scientific publications derived from the game.

name: meQuanics: The Quantum Computer Game
reward_description: You will be provided with a binary version of the physics engine of meQuanics.  The engine is designed to enforce the fundamental physics rules of the game and ensure that your results are scientifically valid.  This engine can be interfaced with other front-end software to create automated players or used to further study and design topological quantum circuits for real world hardware. You get developer access to incorporate custom designed quantum circuits/algorithms within the physics engine binary (circuits can be compiled using our own conversion code from higher level algorithms, or accepted as initial geometric puzzles)

name: meQuanics: The Quantum Computer Game
reward_description: You get limited access to the raw database of meQuanics.  Backers at this level will be allowed access to the optimisation record of up to a maximum of 10 puzzles (quantum circuits) within the meQuanics environment at anytime after the release of the full game and active data collection commences.  Puzzles included can be specific quantum circuits submitted by backers at this level.   Results derived from this access will remain the property of the backers at this pledge level

name: meQuanics: The Quantum Computer Game
reward_description: You get full access to the raw database of meQuanics. This pledge level is aimed at individuals and organisations that wish to use the user data generated from the game to help design compilers and optimisers for surface code quantum architectures. Access to the database will be read only and be for a period of 12 months from the full release of the game, starting from the point where active data collection commences.  Access will include all trackback data on circuit optimisations collected from the clients. This pledge level makes no guarantees regarding the amount of data collected.  We will make every effort to make the game popular and if data collection is initially small, the initial 12 months data collection can be extended and renegotiated on a case-by-case basis. Data provided at this level is provided freely for use in other applications or optimisers.  The meQuanics team will relinquish all IP rights to results derived from data obtained at this pledge level Access to the database beyond the initial 12 months can be further negotiated (with additional fees and/or partnership agreements) with the meQuanics team.

reward_description: An interactive and inspirational webinar by Toke lifting the lid on developing bob. name: Beasts of Burden - a game making it fun to beat stress

All participants are given 3 months free access to the bob app. (excludes related travel costs)

name: Beasts of Burden - a game making it fun to beat stress

(excludes related travel costs)

reward_description: You also get an upgrade in apparel to the second piece of limited edition apparel that is being produced for this Kickstarter campaign, a cool shawl collar rugby featuring an exclusively designed logo for a fictional Los Angeles team. I decided to try and have some fun in deciding what the second team name should be. I'm currently taking any suggestions, if you think you have a cool name that you also know would make a sweet logo, send me your suggestions on Twitter @GmOnFb. In a few days, I'll pick the top five suggestions and I'll put it to a vote, and the Gyula will design a cool logo of the winning name which will adorn the back of the sweatshirt. So not only do you get both versions of the app, a messenger bag, and an invite to the beta besting period, you'll also get a cool and unique piece of clothing that you'll can throw on once the weather starts to get chilly, I am very grateful for your support.

name: Game-On Football
reward_description: You also get the two different pieces of custom apparel being produced for Game-On Football's Kickstarter campaign. You not only get the shawl collar rugby sweatshirt that will feature the LA team logo that is going to be designed by Gyula, but you'll also receive a really cool letterman jacket featuring another exclusive logo designed by Gyula and once again I'm open to suggestions from you guys. Send me your suggestions on Twitter, think you have an even better idea for NY team name, or maybe even London? Send me your suggestions on Twitter @GmOnFb, I'll pick the best ideas and we'll put it to a vote once again. The body of the jacket will be black and 100% wool with black leather sleeves. The knitted collar and cuffs as well as vertical chest pocket will be accented with the main color that will be featured in the final logo design that will be displayed on the back. It's going to be a pretty cool piece of limited edition apparel, and you'll be one of very few in possession of one. Thank you for support!

name: Game-On Football
reward_description: Thank you so much for believing in what I am trying to do with Game-On Football, your support means a lot to me.

I am very grateful believing in Game-On Football.

reward_description: Somebody runs by, brushes you with his briefcase and  yells out something about meeting...son?. A distinct scent of flesh hits you. You  like it enough but the cravings just not there...yet. I sincerely thank you for taking the first whiff. (Pedestrian Rewards): Goal 1

name: Addicted to Zombies: zG1 Virus Project
reward_description: Upon heading for work, you notice a pamphlet on the ground, hoping to find an underdressed female for your immature mind but unfortunately you find...none of it at all, just a weird logo on the front. Curiously you pick it up trying to decipher the first page only to find weird emergency guidelines. A greenish sticky substance was left on your fingers in which you wipe off into a handkerchief. In a hurry, you run off, bumping your briefcase into a pedestrian and yell "Sorry ..meeting...soon." (The Infector Rewards): Hi-def desktop artwork of the game, Bonus Code: Start with in-game currency (set amount TBD). Additional Bonus once activated- Goal 1

name: Addicted to Zombies: zG1 Virus Project
reward_description: *Sniffle* While at work, you sneeze so loud you startle your coworkers. As your nose begins to tingle you instinctively pull out your handkerchief, smother your face into it and sneeze. You sneeze again into the cloth and notice blood along with the mysterious substance from earlier. "Hmm...Blood." You start to lick it. (Bloodlust Rewards): Hi-def desktop artwork, Name in credit section as a backer,, Bonus Code: Start with in-game currency (set amount TBD). Bonus Code: Start with a handgun. name: Derelict - Mobile Ad-Free Multiplayer First Person Shooter
reward_title: Full game development course and more!
reward_description: The first one will be access to the multiplayer testing of the game, during the testing period it won't be part of the main game app, i'll temporarily upload the multiplayer mode in a separate app that will be removed once the testing is complete and multiplayer is ready to be added into the main game, YOU WILL GET ACCESS TO THIS TESTING, i'll send you a promo code to the multiplayer testing app and you will get to play the multiplayer maps before anyone else and give me feedback! The second thing will be a full video streaming of a tutorial/course on how to make a first person shooter using unity! You will learn absolutely everything! From how to get started to how to create the player, enemies, weapons, powerups, maps, realtime events, and much much more! After this course you should be fully capable of making a video game from scratch on your own! The third reward... this game won't be my last game, i have ideas for other games that i will soon create... not only will you get knowledge of that when the time comes but you will also get that next game for free! You have my word! No tengo palabras para expresar mi gratitud, estoy eternamente agradecido... recibirás todas las recompensas anteriores pero igual recibirás 3 cosas muy especiales para mi: La primera será acceso al testing de multijugador de mi juego, dado que multijugador se encuentra en temprano desarrollo y el juego será publicado muy pronto, subiré el modo multijugador de manera temporar en una aplicación separada del juego completo, RECIBIRÁS ACCESO ESPECIAL A DICHA APP, esta app contendrá todos los maravillosos mapas que haya creado y solo será multijugador, esta app solo será para pruebas por lo que solo existirá por el tiempo que yo tome en desarrollar este modo de juego. Recibirás un código para que descarges esa app temporal de prueba, podrás jugar los mapas multijugador antes que los demás y podrás darme comentarios y apoyo! La segunda es un curso/tutorial completo en video streaming en como hacer un juego first person shooter usando unity! Aprenderás absolutamente todo! Desde como empezar a utilizar el software, hasta como crear al jugador, los enemigos, armas, powerups, maps, eventos en tiempo real y mucho mucho mucho más! Despues de este curso deberías ser perfectamente capáz de poder crear un videojuego desde cero por ti mismo! La tercera recompensa... este no será mi último juego, tengo ideas para otros juegos que voy a crear muy pronto! No solo te haré saber detalles de dicho juego antes que nadie sino que tambien lo recibirás completamente gratis! Tienes mi palabra!

name: Warp Lane Online
reward_description: "Join the navy," they said, "and see the galaxy." So far, all you have seen is the inside of the training center, and the inside of your eyelids when they let you sleep. Following good advice, you did what you were told and complained as little as possible. Now you are on your way to your first post, and training for your specialty. You will recieve our everlasting thanks and appreciation, plus your name listed as 'magnificent benefactor' on warplanemedia.com. As one of our benefactors, you will be emailed a link to download an ebook version of Warp Lane I: Storm Clouds Gather. Long life to you and success in all your endeavors!

name: Warp Lane Online
reward_description: Life in the ship yard was starting to get to you, the walls were closing in. Not that a ship would be much different, but at least you would be moving! So you focused on your specialty and minded your own business. Eventually the promotions came, and finally a transfer! You have been assigned to the Youngstown Colony, recently refit as a science ship. Now to explore the galaxy! You will recieve our everlasting thanks and appreciation, plus your name listed as 'magnificent benefactor' on warplanemedia.com. As one of our benefactors, you will be emailed a link to download an ebook version of Warp Lane I. Additionally, you will submit a name for a star in the online game! Name it anything you like, honor permitting.

name: Warp Lane Online
reward_description: You have chosen the officer corps for your career? Well done! Pay attention, study hard, and forget everything you have ever learned before. From now on, the navy will tell you what to think. The navy will be your heart and soul, your family and your love. If you can think quickly, keep a clear head and make decisions, you will go far. As well as being listed as 'magnificent benefactor' you will receive original artwork, a chibi of yourself dressed as an ensign, suitable for framing. Our artist will need a reasonable facsimile or photo, from your facebook page maybe? As one of our benefactors, you will be emailed a link to download an ebook version of Warp Lane I: Storm Clouds Gather.

name: Warp Lane Online
reward_description: Your mother told you there would be days like this! Everywhere you turn, there is someone questioning you and making your very existence a self contradiction! You would think the extra stripe on your sleeve would give you some credibility. Well, think again Second Lieutenant. Keep pressing on: you are commander material. You will be listed as 'magnificent benefactor' and you will receive Warp Lane Book I: Storm Clouds Gather and Book II: To Be Named, actual paper books, both signed by the author. This is just the kind of reading a young officer needs. As one of our benefactors, you will be emailed a link to download an ebook version of Warp Lane I: Storm Clouds Gather.

name: Warp Lane Online
reward_description: The promotion came sooner than you expected. Mom said that it pays to stay busy and keep your mouth shut. Certainly everyone has finally noticed your abilities. You catch your thoughts, realizing your small talent could not possibly explain your rapid promotion. You have been hearing rumors, everyone is unsettled and on edge. You will be listed as 'magnificent benefactor' and you will receive Warp Lane Books I, II and III, actual paper books, each signed by the author. As one of our benefactors, you will be emailed a link to download an ebook version of Warp Lane I: Storm Clouds Gather.

name: Warp Lane Online
reward_description: Good work, Chief! You have stayed ahead of your peers and learned to navigate the systems of the navy. You also have learned a few secrets, and learned how to keep them close. There are even times you can turn the convoluted structure of the navy in your favor. Now for some shore leave and much needed R&R. Have fun. Not too much fun. You will be listed as 'magnificent benefactor' and you will receive Books I & II, signed by the author. As one of our benefactors, you will be emailed a link to download an ebook version of Warp Lane I: Storm Clouds Gather. Best of all, you can have a secret message encrypted in a jpg file in the game! Any reasonable message you would like, honor permitting.

name: Warp Lane Online
reward_description: Well, Commander, you have added 'the bird' to your sleeve, and your soul fairly reeks with authority. You command respect and get things done. The difficult you do immediately, impossible takes a little longer. You finally won respect from that certain master chief as well. Things are definitely going your way, but something is not right... As one of our 'magnificent benefactors,' you will be emailed a link to download an ebook version of Warp Lane I: Storm Clouds Gather. To incite the envy of all your friends, you will be mailed the Limited Edition Warp Lane Board Game, signed by the development team, which is sure to become a collector's item, and a treasured possession.

name: Warp Lane Online
reward_description: Congratulations, Master Chief, very few make it this far. By this point in your career, you have seen and heard everything. Your ability managing people and situations has opened doors. The navy has made you what you are, and now you are returning the favor. Officers salute you and everyone else fears you. Even the captain comes to you for advice. You will receive books I, II, III, & IV  all signed by the author. As one of our benefactors, you will be emailed a link to download an ebook version of Warp Lane I: Storm Clouds Gather. Best of all, you can have a secret message encrypted in a jpg file in the game! Any reasonable message you would like, honor permitting.

name: Warp Lane Online
reward_description: The promotion came ahead of schedule, and you barely had time to celebrate with a few  friends. Everyone is too busy, and no wonder: there is a war on. Everything you know is being challenged. You can barely cope, and you feel driven before a hurricane. But no one sees it on you. You wear the face of the grim warrior. As one of our 'magnificent benefactors,' you will be emailed a link to download an ebook version of Warp Lane I: Storm Clouds Gather. As a commander, you will receive the Limited Edition Warp Lane Board Game, signed by the development team, as well as books I & II signed by the author.

name: Warp Lane Online
reward_description: Your Command. Your Ship. Every room you enter, someone shouts out: "Captain on Deck!" and everyone snaps to attention. They fear you, and  you have their lives in your hands. To you they are not people. They are tools to bring Death to your enemies. But absolutely no one sees your anguished soul, every night in your sleepless, lonely bed. As one of our 'magnificent benefactors,' you will be emailed a link to download an ebook version of Warp Lane I: Storm Clouds Gather. As a captain, you will receive the Limited Edition Warp Lane Board Game, signed by the development team, as well as books I, II, III, & IV all signed by the author.

name: Warp Lane Online
reward_description: You have shown good combat sense, and more than a little good luck. So the Admiralty pushes ships on you, and insults you with impossible missions. In order to keep your sanity, you pretend it is just a game. You resolve to do what needs to be done, no more and no less. In fleeting moments of calm you think about your first love,  and imagine how things might have been. As a benefactor you will receive the ebook version of Warp Lane I: Storm Clouds Gather. You will also receive the Limited Edition Warp Lane Board Game, signed by the development team, as well as books I, II, III, & IV all signed by the author. To sweeten the deal, you will also receive the limited edition Warp Lane Online Tee Shirt!

name: Warp Lane Online
reward_description: Your victory is as certain as the birth of new stars in the stellar nursery, just off the starboard bow. You have committed fleets, each bearing incredible fury, against the strong places of your enemies. You are creating a new galaxy, a galaxy of your design. You know you will win the war, but one thought is nagging you, it bites you when you least expect it: 'Can you win the Peace?' As one of our 'magnificent benefactors,' you will receive an ebook version of Warp Lane I: Storm Clouds Gather. You will receive the Limited Edition Warp Lane Board Game, signed by the development team, as well as books I, II, III, & IV  all signed by the author, as well as limited edition Storm Clouds Gather and Warp Lane Online Tee Shirts!

name: Internal Invasion - a physics game for mobile devices
reward_description: Don't you just love T-Shirts? They just make you all warm and awesome looking, don't they? What's that? You can get an Internal Invasion T-Shirt? Wow, you just made my day! You'll also get rewards 2-8, so feel even better about yourself!

name: Internal Invasion - a physics game for mobile devices
reward_description: Wanted: Awesome level designer for awesome game! Step up to the mark, and show the world what you're capable of. We'll work with you, one on one to see that your level will be designed just the way you want it, and included in the game under the 'bonus' section. We'll also see to it that your name will be displayed alongside the level selection. Includes rewards 2-9

name: Internal Invasion - a physics game for mobile devices
reward_description: Are you a world famous musician? Maybe you're just super talented! Either way, if you've got the skills, we want to hear it! We'll include your track as the background music in the bonus menu of Internal Invasion. *IMPORTANT - MUSIC MUST NOT INCLUDE VOCALS. We'll add your name and track to the credits, as well as another line of your choice. Includes rewards 2-10! *Note, this is a special limited reward, and is not included with other rewards.

name: Internal Invasion - a physics game for mobile devices
reward_description: Not content with designing your own level? How about designing your own boss level? Sound exciting? Well pick your jaw up from the floor, it's true! You get to help design its appearance, as well as how to defeat it! Dream come true? Well, you're welcome! On top of that, you'll have our eternal thanks, as well as rewards 2-10! We'll also throw in a T-Shirt of your boss character in addition to reward 10! *Note, this is a special limited reward, and is not included with other rewards.

name: Internal Invasion - a physics game for mobile devices
reward_description: Feel like making your own version of Internal Invasion? We'll send you all the images, SPRITES, artwork, 3D models, music and sound effects (Currently over 1gb of data) and let you do what you want with them! Feel like making Internal Invasion 2? Well if you've got the ability, you've also got the content necessary! Includes rewards 2-10!

name: Internal Invasion - a physics game for mobile devices
reward_description: You want it? You got it! This reward snags you the code behind the game, as well as rewards 2-13, meaning you can make changes to the original game itself. Want to add more levels, change the ones already in place, or just want an idea of how the game was made? This reward's for you!

name: Internal Invasion - a physics game for mobile devices
reward_description: You'll get a private lesson in the software used to make Internal Invasion, Construct 2. Using the resources you'll gain from rewards 13 and 14, we'll take the steps necessary to help you make a mini-game based on the Internal Invasion mechanics. Take your first steps into becoming a developer yourself! We'll also see to it that you get access to rewards 2 -14, as well as a special T-Shirt as our way of saying thanks, AND... a special mention in the credits as an "EPIC BACKER"!

name: Internal Invasion - a physics game for mobile devices
